NAME:
   loop static - perform on-chain to off-chain swaps using static addresses.

USAGE:
   loop static [command [command options]]

COMMANDS:
   new, n           Create a new static loop in address.
   listunspent, l   List unspent static address outputs.
   listdeposits     Displays static address deposits. A filter can be applied to only show deposits in a specific state.
   listwithdrawals  Display a summary of past withdrawals.
   listswaps        Shows a list of finalized static address swaps.
   withdraw, w      Withdraw from static address deposits.
   summary, s       Display a summary of static address related information.
   in               Loop in funds from static address deposits.
